\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 1
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Daniel k\u233?t\u233? Nebukadnejar warsagh \u225?roene utman\u233?gh sifayan
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
T\u225?f nambiom\u233?n yunj\u233?f njam namndai y\u233?n\u233? warsagh \u225?r Jeyoikimene lim\u225?n\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n k\u233?t\u233? Juda k\u233?nj\u250?n, warsagh \u225?r Nebukadnejar Babilonm\u233?n y\u233?nmorm\u233?n Jerusalem\u233?t a taur\u233?mnau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Yuram yaramai \u225?m\u233?gh muy\u233? y\u233?menat warsagh \u225?r Jeyoyakim t\u233?morw\u233?n Judam\u233?n a y\u233?mndai f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t so tangng\u233?rsau \u225?mb utman\u233?gh rokar k\u233?tam\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngota. F\u233?yo Nebukadnejaram y\u233?n\u233? tarsau k\u233?t\u225?n Babilon mband a k\u233?nj\u250? ekmai k\u233?t\u233? yane ng\u225?nj\u225?n mani ngonj\u233?l m\u233?ngon.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo warsagh \u225?rom yafaretai Asfenaj, yane frondefif ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r, m\u233?n\u225?t so tan\u233?mnjau k\u233?t\u225?n warsagh \u225?roene sifayat \u225?mb tot\u233?r ambum Israilm\u233?n tamorw\u233?n warsagh \u225?rm\u233?n f\u233?r\u233?k ambum a tuk y\u233?tkw\u233?nm\u233?n ambum m\u233?r\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u225? norayai, "Takafangi m\u233? f\u225?ro, s\u233?fakwro ambumm\u233?n f\u233?r\u233?k ambum a mer s\u225?fot tot\u233?r ambum. Kor aem mer s\u233?nt\u233? mwighaf\u233? mat yam tambnaf\u233? a mer moghaf\u233?, a kanfangi fifi \u225?s\u225?fogh\u233?t warsagh \u225?roene m\u233?ngo sifayat. Ewatametati y\u233?n\u233? tot\u233?r ambum Babilon sie a si m\u233?njm\u233?nj watamegh Babilonm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
