W\u233?nde Daniel\u233?m mwigh\u233? y\u233?faronam yau so m\u225?m\u225?fi kawafrotau m\u233?naye njamke a wain ewaramai y\u233?fe y\u233?mo warsagh \u225?rom. Y\u233?mo y\u233?motai ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfene s\u233?nko \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t mat si s\u225?i tanangai yau so taumyongai y\u233?n\u233? afreng\u233?ghofnar njamke. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?nam\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n t\u233? yaramai ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rfene s\u233?nko \u225?roe utman\u233?gh a mwighat yawindam Danielenem\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
W\u233?nde f\u225? m\u233? namyoi, "Y\u233?nd f\u233?rf\u233?r w\u233?m tane yuranem\u233?n a warsagh \u225?roenem\u233?n, emo t\u233? w\u233?nmafareta m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?mo so enete y\u233?n\u233? njamke a wain. Njam f\u233?m k\u233?namnd\u233? s\u225?f \u225?t\u225?mbar\u233?ghare a sotk\u233?f njam fene anoghtar ambumaf\u233? y\u233?nd f\u233?rf\u233?r w\u233?m warsagh \u225?rom so kafngong\u233? y\u233?nd."
