Daniel norayai, "Gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? mato t\u233?nmufongi 10 efogh kw\u233?fro ndau njamkeyan a nu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
K\u233?t\u233? 10 efogh kw\u233?f njam kefongi, y\u233?nfandati t\u225?f nder\u233? s\u225?fot y\u233?nd so n\u233?retam y\u233?nmutanati \u225?mb tot\u233?r ambumaf\u233? emofem enetat warsagh \u225?roene njamke. F\u233?yo f\u233?monyo t\u225?f mwigh\u233? yafrota y\u233?n\u233? kwayaghayan f\u233?mo n\u233?m\u233? njam y\u233?fanda." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
