Warsagh \u225?roene uw\u233?rman\u233?gh siy\u233?m f\u233?yotarofnar. Yau \u225?mb efe m\u233? y\u233?mofemro ng\u225?nj\u225?nng\u225?nj\u225?namro so n\u233?maufrotat fene onjom\u233?n, a f\u225? y\u233?naayau emor \u225?rf\u233?."
