Y\u233?n\u233? s\u233?mb\u225?ran kwankwane yam s\u225?f\u233?t yakmai Daniele gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?ghe. F\u233?yo Daniel tuyotau njafarm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
