Y\u233?monyo elimnde yam mband maratan n\u233?m\u233? nufrotat; y\u233?mofem engwit\u233?rmbote warsagh \u225?r a engwasote \u225?mb warsagh \u225?r. Y\u233?mo ewaramete k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? y\u233?fe efe em k\u225?fet\u233? a mat yam a f\u225? y\u233?fe efe m\u233? ndimbal skul mat yam a f\u225? t\u233?fn\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Y\u233?mo s\u225?f\u233?t en\u233?kmete k\u233?njkam a s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam a mat y\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? kw\u233?fitayan y\u233?k\u233?m, t\u233? kwayaghayam yarendam f\u225?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?ndo k\u225?njo n\u233?marametan a n\u233?marsan, o Ng\u225?nj\u225?n tane \u225?kifene, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo t\u233? waramai ta k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? a muy\u233?. F\u233?mo t\u233? waufro ta n\u233?mat y\u233?nd k\u243?mnendan fefaf a s\u225?f\u233?t y\u233?k\u233?m t\u233?fefaf n\u233?mat warsagh \u225?r kw\u225?ur\u233?mnau."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Daniel\u233?m onjo tafenau
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
F\u233?yo Daniel n\u233?ngwanoi ya fandagh\u233?t Ariok, efe t\u233? yafaretai warsagh \u225?rom m\u233?n\u225?t so tasmetaw\u233?t k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? t\u233?fn\u225?r Babilonm\u233?n. Daniel norayai y\u225?faf, "Yau esmeta k\u233?rot k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? \u225?r. K\u233?ng\u233?mnja k\u233?t\u225?n warsagh \u225?roefaf, a y\u233?ndo so yaufrotan y\u225?njo onjoene fifi."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Ariok\u233?m w\u233?keye y\u233?ng\u233?mnjam Daniel k\u233?t\u225?n warsagh \u225?roefaf a norayai, "Y\u233?ndo t\u233? yinjon \u225?mb wer\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r Judam\u233?n emo so t\u233?mndang\u233? warsagh \u225?r s\u225?i yafene yane onjo!"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Warsagh \u225?rom t\u233?mndang\u233? Daniel(o \u225?mb y\u233?tkw\u233?n Beltesajar), "Y\u233?n\u233? efalo f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m? F\u233?yotaro f\u233?mo so waufrong\u233? ta n\u233?m\u233? tane onjo t\u233?m a n\u233?m\u233? yane fifi y\u233?m?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Daniel yawangoi, "Y\u233?na yau em k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? \u225?r, ngamangam\u233? t\u233?fn\u225?r, f\u233?r\u233?k suf\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r, o yunj\u233?f fandagh t\u233?fn\u225?ram emofem so s\u225?f\u233?t tufanaw\u233?t warsagh \u225?roene kwankwane yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?na f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?n njafaran emo s\u225?f\u233?t\u233? eufane kwankwane yam, a y\u233?mo t\u233? yauyafo warsagh \u225?r Nebukanejar n\u233?m\u233? so n\u225?tyane soram\u233? yuwon. S\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndo so nemaufrotan fene onjom\u233?n a gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?ghe n\u233?m\u233? tafande njam k\u233?malinjo fenjo yameyan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
"Njam fene sari t\u233?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n, f\u233?mo onjo n\u233?kmang\u233?rm\u233?n yam ndern\u225?ye so en\u233?m. F\u225? emo s\u225?f\u233?t ekmete kwankwane yam t\u233? k\u233?mauyote n\u233?m\u233? so natyanat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
A y\u233?n\u233? yau y\u233?m m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd kar w\u233?m k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? k\u233?r ro a ewaindan \u225?mb \u225?r nden\u233? y\u233?nd mat w\u233?m kwankwane yam fene onjom\u233?n, w\u233?nde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n f\u225? m\u233?nde m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?m fem s\u225?i mat k\u225?y\u225?to n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m fene tikfan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Fene gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?ghan fene sari, f\u233?mo k\u233?s yinjoi takayong\u233?rw\u233?n fer\u233?re ndimbal, \u225?l\u225?l\u233?ghaf\u233? \u225?r s\u225?f mbanmban y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?morw\u233?n f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? mbanmban. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r s\u225?f mbanmbanoene s\u233?nko st\u233?morw\u233?n yafrotam\u233?nd m\u233?nam\u233?n freng\u233?ghkaf golm\u233?n, yane w\u233?t a s\u233?rakw tanmorw\u233?n silfam\u233?n, yane fut a burab\u233?r tamorw\u233?n bronj tot t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
Yane kafkaf tamorw\u233?n n\u225?fgheyay\u233?nd ng\u233?nd a tot t\u233?f\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
Njam t\u233?fandau, w\u233?m n\u233?nanfai k\u233?tam\u233? mband tunak\u233?fta, w\u233?nde yau yafrotam \u225?rfifi ng\u225?ngayam. Y\u233?nayam esmai ng\u233?nd a tot t\u233?f\u233?n kafkaf, etyanam n\u233?mbnar kar\u233?fkar\u233?f tawafrotau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
M\u233?inyotio \u225?r s\u225?f mbanmban siyomorm\u233?n y\u233?tyanam k\u233?t\u225?notio n\u233?mbnar tot t\u233?f\u233?n kar\u233?fkar\u233?f t\u233?rt\u233?r, ngendm\u233?n, bronjm\u233?n, silfam\u233?n, a golm\u233?n. F\u233?yo mbormboram eng\u233?fnjai ndenam\u233? ronjaghofnar ndenanit ngw\u233?rm\u233?ng tum\u225?ng\u233?gh sifayam\u233?. W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?m \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam yirory\u233?ng \u225?r s\u225?f mbanmban n\u233?nayatoi ndimbal mband tunak\u233?f \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?nayam yafary\u233?ng m\u233?inyotio mband.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233?t t\u233?morw\u233?n onjo. S\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndfem so taufrong\u233?m warsagh \u225?roe n\u233?m\u233? yane fifi y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Fene sari, f\u233?m n\u233?m minde ndimbalfifi k\u233?tam\u233? \u225?mb warsagh \u225?r k\u233?s em. Njafarm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam t\u233? n\u233?maramai tuk sifay\u233? waft\u233?, muy\u233?, a atman\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Y\u233?mo t\u233? niy\u225?toi lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r m\u233?inyotio mband y\u225?njo rokarafayo a w\u233?i t\u233? ekmetam k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?r a men fene waft\u233? mbandmbanan. F\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?m golm\u233?n k\u233?s y\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
"W\u233?nde y\u233?mo soram\u233? fene warsagh \u225?r lim\u225?ng\u233?gh \u225?nde njam yiy\u225?to, \u225?mb lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? ndimbal yu so y\u233?m nden\u233? kor yau fem k\u233?s k\u233?n\u233?m, so kangong\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t tang\u233? fene sifay\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? y\u233?n\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? yu njam kuyang\u233?, w\u233?i so y\u233?m \u225?mb nambiom\u233?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? yu, y\u233?n\u233? so fiy\u233?m bronj t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n k\u233?s y\u233?m, so kokayong\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t mband marat so y\u233?limnde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? yu s\u225?i t\u233?nmaitong\u233? so y\u233?n\u233?m 4m\u233?n nden\u233? muyaf\u233? tot t\u233?f\u233?n. Y\u233?n\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? yuam so engfamngote a eng\u233?tyane m\u233?inyotio njam t\u233?smang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
Kafkaf a s\u233?nko ndamb f\u233?mo \u225?rk\u233? t\u233? tafande tarw\u233?n m\u233?nam\u233?n tot t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n a ng\u233?ndm\u233?n, tyafotau nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? yu so em f\u233?nataye. Nden\u233? t\u233?f\u233?n k\u233?s wanjm\u233?ghkaf ere ng\u233?ndaf\u233?, so w\u233?i yam \u225?mb muy\u233? tot t\u233?f\u233?nta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
W\u233?nde \u225?mb kar\u233?fta so y\u233?m muyaf\u233? nden\u233? yame tot t\u233?f\u233?n, \u225?mb kar\u233?fta so y\u233?m muyafnar nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? ng\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? af\u233?ghkaf tot t\u233?f\u233?n a ng\u233?nd w\u233?i yuyafote nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? yu y\u233?ta so muy\u233? naram\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?yan s\u225?i y\u233?ngwafrotat ew\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh yam y\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?n m\u233?r\u233?s awer\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. W\u233?nde f\u225? yau so nakayotat kaka m\u233?rne nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? tot t\u233?f\u233?n a ng\u233?nd yau so kawanjmetangend.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? warsagh \u225?rfene lim\u225?n\u233?gh yu soram\u233?, njafarm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam so yeite \u225?mb lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? yu \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? yau so tirorngi o taindang\u233?. Y\u233?nayam so m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? yu engwirone yau so em, a so yakai tuot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? fiy\u233?m yane fifi w\u233?m \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? t\u233? n\u233?nanfai k\u233?tam\u233? mband tunak\u233?fta, yau \u225?r ng\u225?ngayam yafrotam, y\u233?n\u233? sirory\u233?ng kar\u233?fkar\u233?f tafrotau y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r s\u225?f mbanmban tot t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n, bronj tot t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n, ng\u233?ndm\u233?n, silfam\u233?n a golm\u233?n. Ndimbal Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam y\u233?n\u233? tauyafotau warsagh \u225?roe n\u233?m\u233? so nufrotat soram\u233? yuwon. Onjo siy\u233?m efalo a yane fifi mwighat y\u233?m."
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Nebukadnejar\u233?m fai yafrotam Daniel
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 46\~}
F\u233?yo warsagh \u225?r Nebkadneja nuyai f\u225?yo yuot Daniele r\u233?re a y\u225?wefnoi, a Nebukadnejaram ewafaretai y\u225?njo \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t taramangy\u233?nd gh\u233?ng\u233?n a tawarongay\u233?nd m\u233?ndef\u233? ng\u233?ng\u233?n yane r\u233?re. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 47\~}
Warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?mndai Daniel, "Efalofifi, fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n siy\u233?m minde ndimbalfifi \u225?mb ng\u225?nj\u225?n tamb\u233?n, warsagh \u225?rfene Yur\u233?, s\u233?lngw\u233?laf\u233? yam\u233?n fenagh t\u233?fn\u225?r, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m f\u233?yotaro k\u233?n\u233?m t\u233? tafene y\u233?n\u233? kwankwane yam."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 48\~}
F\u233?yo warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?kafai Daniel tuk \u225?s\u225?fogh sifayat a yaramai t\u225?rf\u225?r ndimbalero ram\u233?gh rokar. Y\u233?mo yiy\u225?toi Daniel lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r Babilon\u233?n \u225?mb mband kw\u233?ndfaf, a k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? s\u233?nko \u225?r m\u233?inyotio Nebnadnejarane k\u225?fet\u233? mwigh\u233? t\u233?fn\u225?r tamorw\u233?n yuanyo. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 49\~}
Danielene \u243?mneng\u233?ghan warsagh \u225?rom ekafai Sadrak, Mesak, a Abednego s\u225?i tamorw\u233?n Babilon\u233?n mband kw\u233?ndkw\u233?nd fandagh \u225?r, Daniel w\u233?nde t\u233?morw\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? warsagh \u225?roene sifayan.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 3
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Nebukadnejarene golm\u233?n \u225?r s\u225?f mbanmban
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Warsagh \u225?r Nebukadnejaram yafrotam golm\u233?n \u225?r s\u225?f 90 fit tomb\u233? tukta 90 fit marat a yeitam k\u233?t\u233? Babilon\u233?n \u225?mb mband kw\u233?ndkw\u233?ndfaf fanfnero Duran. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?mo si y\u233?ngowatembai k\u233?t\u225?n tuk ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?rafefaf, ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, gafana \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r, wawanjagh \u225?r, mani wanjeng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r, mogh t\u233?fn\u225?r n\u225?k t\u233?fn\u225?r, a m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? mband kw\u233?ndkw\u233?nd sat\u233? f\u233?nataye k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t so tanmorw\u233?n s\u225?i tatetaw\u233?t y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?f mbanmban \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?mo yitam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? ofis \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r enmorm\u233?n kokayotaw\u233?t \u225?r sof mbanmban r\u233?re \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? warsagh \u225?r Nebkadnejaram y\u233?itam.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
F\u233?yo mat si t\u233?fn\u225?r n\u233?ngutuai, "\u193?r m\u233?inyotio f\u233?nataye ngar a ndimbal f\u233?natayero yum\u233?n a f\u233?nataye si t\u233?fn\u225?r n\u233?n\u225?y\u225?retati warsagh \u225?roene wafargh\u233?t! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Njam f\u233?mofem t\u225?y\u225?rangi suf\u233?r ke, flut, jita, laire, af, faif, a \u225?mb kembne rokar k\u233?s, n\u225?wefnotati mbandot m\u233?n\u225?t so y\u225?wefnotati warsagh \u225?r Nebukadnejarene golm\u233?n \u225?r s\u225?f mban mbanmbanoe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
\u193?rk\u233? \u225?r njam kakenang\u233? yau s\u225?i k\u225?y\u225?rang\u233? so w\u233?keye yitat k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?r\u233?nj f\u233?s\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
Kembne rokar keyan, m\u233?inyotio \u225?r, n\u233?m\u233? ngar n\u233?m o ndimbal yum\u233?n o n\u233?m\u233? si t\u233?fn\u225?r, n\u233?itatati mbandot a y\u225?wefnotati golm\u233?n \u225?r s\u225?f mbanmbanoe \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? warsagh \u225?r Nebukadnejar\u233?m y\u233?itam.
