M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? t\u233? n\u225?ke y\u233?ramay\u233?nd y\u233?mofem si r\u233?sagh \u225?r\u233?m; y\u233?n\u233? wafar\u233?ghan t\u233? y\u233?kmangi y\u233?mofem nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar \u225?r\u233?m, m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio \u225?r so mat em nden\u233? minde tuk\u233?n \u225?rom elimnde lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? mband maratan. Y\u233?mo ewaramete ende t\u233?u efe y\u233?mo t\u233?kafang\u233? t\u233?u em yuan \u225?r.
