Beltesajar, y\u233?n\u233? onjof t\u233?m nden\u233? y\u233?nd warsagh \u225?r Nebukadnejar t\u233?m. S\u233?nonjo kwaufro n\u233?m\u233? yane fifi y\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n yau \u225?mb kafeta mwigh\u233? t\u233?fn\u225?r tane lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233?an em s\u225?i yafrotat y\u233?n\u233?. W\u233?nde f\u233?mo so kwaufro ta m\u233?nam\u233?n nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar ng\u225?nj\u225?nafene mb\u233?rmb\u233?r siy\u233?m fene k\u233?nj\u250?n.
