Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?y\u225?rghan, Daniel(w\u233?i \u225?mb y\u233?tkw\u233?n tamotaw\u233?t Betesajar)y\u225?indam \u225?mb efoghf\u233?nf\u233?ne, f\u233?rf\u233?rot yawindam onjoene fifi waferegham. F\u233?yo warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?mndai f\u225?, Beltesajar yau mwighat n\u233?mawinda onjoam a n\u233?m\u233? yane fifi wafer\u233?gh y\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "Betesajar\u233?m yawangoi, y\u233?nd nemnan yam \u225?tyar\u233?ghm\u233?n eufarote y\u233?n\u233? onjoam so nufrotat fene s\u233?nan\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?rafefaf, tane yur\u233?, a yau fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
W\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? f\u233?mo \u225?rk\u233? t\u233?fande kanote minde tomb\u233? a muyaro, t\u225?yanje njafar tuk\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?inyotio mband maratan s\u225?i t\u233?fandau. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Y\u233?naoene tamorw\u233?n mer tot\u233?r w\u233?n \u225?rau ngarot arau a mbwe k\u233?r ro t\u233?morw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t \u225?r\u233?m so t\u233?netaw\u233?t. K\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?r t\u225?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n yane njaran, a men nj\u233?n karametaw\u233?t yane kafekafeyam\u233?.
