Y\u233?n\u233? w\u233?n, fene sari siy\u233?m f\u233?m. M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m t\u233? k\u233?n\u233?m ndimbal a muy\u233? k\u233?r ro. Fene ndimbalfifi t\u233? karmbote tuk\u233?t k\u233?t\u225?n njafarot, a lim\u225?n\u233?gh y\u233?nam\u233? mband \u225?rkam\u233? y\u233?ny\u225?to. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?mo yinjoi si r\u233?sagh \u225?r, nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar \u225?r, k\u233?newonau njafarta a korayau, "T\u233?nfetangi w\u233?n a t\u233?nwalindangi. W\u233?nde krongi t\u233?f\u233?n a s\u233?r\u233?mb k\u233?s em mbandan, yumbetati marat tot t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n a bronj tot t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n \u225?ng\u233?ghe a t\u233?rendaw\u233?t mer mulmulaf\u233? yusam. Tumyongi f\u225? so njafarm\u233?n es f\u233?tram y\u233?ramete. Tumyo f\u225? so y\u233?mor w\u233?r\u225?raf\u233? yus n\u233?ne sifayan 7 yunj\u233?f f\u233?nef\u233?net.
