Nden\u233? y\u233?n\u233? onjoene fifi y\u233?m, fene sari, a n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? minde tuk\u233?n \u225?rom efalo yiy\u225?to so nufrota y\u233?nan tane yurafaf a warsagh \u225?roefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
F\u233?m so nayu kamnd\u233? \u225?rta a f\u233?m so n\u233?mor k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?rafene yus ne sifayam\u233?. F\u233?mo so enete yus ndenanit kau, a f\u233?m so njafar es f\u233?t\u233?ram n\u233?ramete. 7 yunj\u233?f f\u233?nef\u233?ne so kawandang\u233? t\u225?f f\u233?m m\u233? so n\u233?mor nden\u233? ende, k\u233?t\u225?notio f\u233?m mat k\u225?y\u225?to nden\u233? minde tuk\u233?n \u225?rom elimnde lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? yam mband maratan a ewaramete ende t\u233?u y\u233?mo efe t\u233?kafang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
W\u233?nde t\u233?f\u233?n a s\u233?r\u233?mb w\u233?noene \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? nafrangongi mbandan. Nden\u233? yane fifi y\u233?m f\u233?mo so tango fenjo lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? w\u233?ikor njam f\u233?m mat kayato nden\u233? njafaram y\u233?limnde. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Warsagh \u225?r Nebukadnejar, gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? tumyo tane wawanjagh si. K\u233?kmbo yaufiyamta a ewafrota n\u233?m\u233? em mbark\u225?nd. Kafalo k\u233?tam\u233? fene t\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r yam k\u233?s tan\u233?m a gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisaf\u233? t\u225?f n\u233?m yauyau \u225?rfefaf. F\u233?yo f\u233?m t\u225?f m\u233? so n\u233?ngwainde manian.
