Njam f\u225? n\u233?ngretai y\u233?nam\u233? ndimbal tesenta, f\u225? norayai, f\u233?fandangi y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal tesen Babilon! Tane waft\u233? muyaye, y\u233?ndo t\u233? y\u233?rametam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? mer ndimbal tesen nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? tane warsagh \u225?r sifay\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t so yuyafotan tane sarioene kwayagh\u233?.
