Njam y\u233?n\u233? si m\u233? tamorw\u233?n yane s\u233?nf\u233?neyan, ke y\u233?nmorm\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? njafarta, 'O warsagh \u225?r Nebukadnejar, y\u233?n\u233? si siy\u233?m feyot! F\u233?m yau s\u233?nonjo n\u233?m lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233?an. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
F\u233?m so k\u233?mit\u233?rmbongi \u225?rfe tamb\u233?n. F\u233?m so emor k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?rafene yus n\u233?ne sifayam\u233?, a f\u233?mo so enete yus ndenanit kau. 7 yunj\u233?f efoghf\u233?nef\u233?ne so kawaindangi, nden\u233? ende f\u233?m siya n\u233?mor, k\u233?t\u225?notio f\u233?m mat kamnd\u233? nden\u233? minde tuk\u233?n \u225?rom lim\u225?n\u233?gh yafrote lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifay\u233? mband maratam\u233? a ewaramete ende t\u233?u y\u233?mo efe takafang\u233?!
