Y\u233?n\u233? efoghf\u233?nef\u233?neyanyo mogh efalo n\u225?y\u225?toi, a Nebukadnejar yit\u233?rmboy\u233?nd \u225?rf\u233? tamb\u233?n. Y\u233?mo tanetau yus ndenanit kau, a f\u225? njafarm\u233?n es f\u233?tram fuslat tiy\u225?totaw\u233?t. F\u225? nden\u225?ye ende y\u233?morang\u233?rm\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?notio yane s\u233?f kor tomb\u233? n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd ndenanit ndikakafene s\u233?f a yane ng\u225?ng\u233? sot ndenanit m\u233?nafene ng\u225?ng\u233? sot.
