W\u233?nde njam warsagh \u225?roene amafom n\u225?y\u225?rai n\u233?m\u233? yam katyanau, f\u225? w\u233?keye n\u233?ngaflai njamke n\u233?ne m\u233?ngofaf, y\u233?mo t\u233?mndang\u233? Belsajar, gh\u233?rs\u233? tomb\u233? warsagh \u225?r! Yau n\u233?kwam n\u233?rameta a n\u233?m f\u233?rf\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?na y\u233?m \u225?rfene warsagh \u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?gh k\u233?nj\u250?n endene k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?nau nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar ng\u225?nj\u225?nafene mb\u233?rmb\u233?r. T\u225?f Nebukadnejar\u233?m njam t\u233?limndau, y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r finjoy\u233?nd fenagh mwighaf\u233? mat yamaf\u233? a k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? ndenanit ng\u225?nj\u225?n k\u233?s em. Fene fronde \u225?s\u225?fogh r\u233?sagh \u225?r f\u225? warsagh \u225?r fene fronde \u225?s\u225?fogh r\u233?sagh \u225?r warsagh \u225?r Nebukadnejar\u233?m yiy\u225?to fronde \u225?r m\u233?inyotio f\u233?r\u233?k suf\u233?gh \u225?rfeta, ngamangam\u233? \u225?rta, njafar nek\u233?rnek\u233?r mat yam ronjafgh \u225?rfeta a k\u225?fet\u233? si afrogh \u225?rfeta Babilonm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r Daniel, ende warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramai Beltesajar y\u233?m amyogh yamaf\u233? a mer mat yam afoghare y\u233?m a matro y\u233?m. Y\u233?mo so ewafene onjo, s\u225?f\u233?t ekmeta atambar\u233?gh yam a so efene t\u225?ik\u233?raf\u233? k\u233?rt\u233?. Kamota Daniele m\u233?n\u225?t a y\u233?mo so k\u233?maufrong\u233? fe n\u233?m\u233? f\u233?r\u233?noene fifi y\u233?m."
