F\u233?yo Daniel y\u233?nmasroy\u233?nd warsagh \u225?r sof r\u233?re. Warsagh \u225?rom y\u233?motai, "F\u233?m f\u233?t\u233? n\u233?m Daniel, \u225?mb d\u225?bi \u225?r ewanai k\u233?tam\u233? Juda y\u233?mo tane fronde \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?rom, warsagh \u225?r Nebukadnejar\u233?m? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
