Ta t\u233? waufrongi nden\u233? f\u233?mo so f\u233?yotaro yafene a efena t\u225?ik\u233?raf\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? yam. T\u233?u ewafta y\u233?n\u233? si a kwaufro y\u233?naoene fifi n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m\u233?, f\u233?m so nemamanetat nd\u233?nd\u225?k ngarot tomb\u233? s\u225?l\u225?meye warsagh \u225?rfene utma\u233?ghe a f\u233?m so n\u233?m golm\u233?n seinaf\u233? k\u233?mam\u233? fefaf so yumbang. F\u233?m so k\u233?namnda nambiom\u233?n tuk lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r warsagh \u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?ghan.
