Daniel\u233?m tawanong\u233? warsagh \u225?roe, tawer m\u233?n fene ram\u233?gh o taram t\u233?u \u225?m \u225?roe, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndo so k\u233?maufron n\u233?m\u233? faroghm\u233?n fifi y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Fene sari, Minde Tuk\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewaramete minde tuk\u233?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh, sari, ndimbal kwayagh\u233?, a utman\u233?gh k\u233?t\u225?n ene fronde \u225?s\u225?fogh r\u233?sagh \u225?roefaf, Nebukadnejarefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?mo yiyatoi f\u225? minde ndimbalfifi nden\u233? f\u233?nat\u233? \u225?r s\u225?f m\u233?inyotio a ndimbal yu k\u233?s r\u233?ng\u233?m a si f\u233?natayero ngernger tamorw\u233?n yane r\u233?re f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? y\u233?mo k\u233?rot tasmetau f\u225? efe yane m\u233?ndeyan tamorw\u233?n k\u233?rot ngiot a gh\u233?rs\u233? taw\u233?rtongai f\u225? efe yane m\u233?ndeyan tamorw\u233?n gh\u233?rs\u233? s\u225?i taw\u233?rtongai. Y\u233?mo taut\u233?mndau f\u225? efe yane m\u233?ndeyan tamorw\u233?n utman\u233?gh\u233?t a \u225?uw\u233?ghofnar t\u225?y\u225?tongai f\u225? efe yane m\u233?ndeyan tamorw\u233?n s\u225?i \u225?uw\u233?ghofnar t\u225?y\u225?tongai. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
W\u233?nde njam yane tik\u233?f a mwigh\u233? wanjmeghkaf tamorw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?yan f\u225? kar merfifi t\u233?morw\u233?n \u225?mb \u225?rta, f\u225? t\u233? y\u233?nmewory\u233?nd yuot k\u233?tam\u233? yane warsagh \u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?mnjogh sifayata a y\u233?nfay\u233?nd yane ndimbal kwayagh\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
F\u225? t\u233? yit\u233?rmboy\u233?nd k\u233?tam\u233? \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?nta. Y\u225? yaramay\u233?nd k\u233?ghat w\u233?r\u225?rafene mwigh\u233? s\u225?f, a f\u225? y\u233?fefafm\u233? t\u233?kmang\u233?rw\u233?n k\u233?ghat ndonkiafefaf. Y\u233?mo tanetau yus ndenanit kau, a f\u225? fuslat tiy\u225?totaw\u233?t njafar es f\u233?t\u233?ram, k\u233?t\u225?notio warsagh \u225?rfene lim\u225?n\u233?gh yam mband maratan a tauyafong\u233? efe t\u233?u yane m\u233?ndeyan m\u233?n\u225?t f\u225? siya elimnda.
