M\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mo t\u233? tuktukan yau tiy\u225?rete njafarm\u233?n Yur\u233? a t\u233? tam y\u233?n\u233? kafusi k\u233?tam\u233? yane w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngota ewanay\u233?nd fene s\u225?fan. F\u233?m a fene tuk \u225?r k\u233?s em a amaf a \u225?mb kayogh amafam t\u233? tanetat wain y\u233?nata njam taw\u233?rsaw\u233?t silfam\u233?n ng\u225?nj\u225?n, golm\u233?n, bronjm\u233?n, tot t\u233?f\u233?nm\u233?n, w\u233?nm\u233?n, a w\u237?mm\u233?n ng\u225?nj\u225?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rk\u233? yau n\u233?retat yau n\u225?y\u225?retat a yam \u225?mb mat em n\u233?mam\u233?n. W\u233?nde f\u233?mo yau tut\u233?mnde Ng\u225?nj\u225?n emo n\u233?maramete gh\u233?rs\u233? \u225?mbone a y\u233?ngwarawene fene \u225?ligh! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
