"W\u233?nde nde kotam so m\u233? taindang\u233? mogh, a m\u233?inyotio waft\u233? yane so takawangi f\u233?yotio tirorngi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
