Y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m fronde Dariusene lim\u225?n\u233?ghm\u233?n Medem\u233?n \u225?r efe t\u233?morw\u233?n Aasuerusene ambum, efe n\u233?namndai warsagh \u225?r Babilon \u225?rfene. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
T\u225?f yane fronde yunj\u233?f lim\u225?n\u233?ghan, y\u233?nd, Daniel, mat n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? Yurane si wafeghta, \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? t\u233? y\u233?kmai saf\u233?n Jeremay\u225?faf Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r, nden\u233? Jerusalem so y\u233?k\u233?m fanfnero k\u233?t\u225?n 70 yunj\u233?f. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?nd n\u233?nawengoy\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf a Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh sian nakmeyay\u233?m a awafarman\u233?ghan y\u233?maf\u233?. Y\u233?nd w\u233?i kwawong\u233?rw\u233?n yaufi s\u225?l\u225?me a k\u225?f\u233?ghanaw\u233?n y\u233?ndio fake. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
