\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "O Yur\u233?, f\u233?m n\u233?m ndimbal a f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n! F\u233?mo t\u225?f t\u250?m\u233?n ewafrote fene r\u233?ny\u233?ghm\u233?n yam a n\u233?mak\u225?i m\u233? fene uny\u233?ghofnar siam\u233? kw\u233?njtafnar uw\u233?ghan y\u233?fefaf emofem n\u233?muwetat f\u233?m a n\u233?ngayaretat fene wafarogh si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
W\u233?nde y\u233?nd t\u233? yaufiyam kufarotam a yafrotang\u233?m m\u225?m\u225?fi. Y\u233?nd t\u233? namndang\u233?m \u225?y\u225?roghofnar fe tamb\u233?n a takarotaw\u233?t fene wafar\u233?gh si a n\u225?kn\u225?k. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?nd t\u233? nakenay\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u225?y\u225?rangay\u233?m fene \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r Ngnajan mat y\u225?togh \u225?r, efe korayaw\u233?t fene muyayan k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?fene warsagh \u225?rfefaf a tuk \u225?rfefaf a akafefaf a k\u233?t\u225?n m\u233?inyotio \u225?rfefaf mbandan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
"Yur\u233?, f\u233?m n\u233?m mbark\u225?nd k\u233?nj\u250?n; w\u233?nde njam f\u233?mo y\u233?fanda, t\u233?fene s\u225?f sem ewafne w\u225?iw\u225?iam. Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m efalo y\u233?m m\u233?inyotio t\u233?fenem\u233?n, y\u233?mafayo Judam\u233?n \u225?r k\u233?s em a Jerusalemm\u233?n a m\u233?inyotio Israilm\u233?n, kofarnat kaka a nayu \u225?ndan f\u233?mo t\u233? y\u233?nmafaretam n\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?fene \u225?y\u225?roghofnar t\u233?fnan fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
O Yur\u233?, y\u233?nd a t\u233?fne warsagh \u225?r k\u233?s em, tuk \u225?r, a \u225?kif w\u225?iw\u225?i y\u233?nmafne m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem t\u233? yaufiyam tawafrotam fefaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
W\u233?nde Yur\u233? t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n siy\u233?m gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? k\u233?r ro a yaufiyam wigh \u225?r ndemam\u233?n yau tiy\u225?retam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?ndfem yau tiy\u225?retam Yur\u233? t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, y\u233?ndfem yau tawaitotam fene wawanjagh si y\u233?mo \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?nmaramai y\u225?njo \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?raf\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r efe tamorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
M\u233?inyotio Israil \u225?r yau n\u225?y\u225?rangi fene wawanjagh sifaf a s\u233?m n\u233?mawengongi, kakenat yau k\u225?y\u225?retat fene k\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n sotaf\u233? mb\u225?w\u225?rm\u233?n a moghm\u233?n k\u233?s ekai Mosesene n\u225?kan, Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r, t\u233? yasury\u233?ng t\u233?fefaf m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?fene yaufiyam t\u233?fnan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
F\u233?mo t\u233? tawaitote fenjo si a tawafrote t\u233?fefaf a t\u233?fene lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?rafefaf w\u233?i t\u233?nmawongoste y\u233?nd. Yau \u225?mb k\u233?t\u233? nden\u233? kaukau t\u233?morw\u233?n natyary\u233?ng Jerusalemm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
M\u233?inyotio mb\u225?w\u225?rm\u233?n ekai t\u233?fene Mosesene n\u225?k k\u233?nj\u250?n t\u233? efalo n\u225?y\u225?toy\u233?nd. W\u233?nde y\u233?nd t\u233? nakenay\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i konendaw\u233?m gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisat k\u233?t\u225?n Yur\u233? t\u233?fene ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf m\u233?n\u225?yan s\u225?i kawengotaw\u233?m t\u233?fene yaufiyamta a mat k\u225?y\u225?totaw\u233?m yane efalo si. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?nnde Yuram t\u233? y\u233?n\u233?rsam t\u233?fefaf kaukau \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?mo y\u233?frendam. Yur\u233? t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n mbark\u225?nd t\u233?morw\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? yam stawafrotau, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?ndfem yau yiy\u225?ray\u233?m.
