"O Yur\u233? t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, f\u233?mo y\u233?n\u233?rsam tuot utman\u233?gh fene y\u233?tkw\u233?nfaf m\u233?n\u225?yan eutory\u233?ng fenjo \u225?r k\u233?tam\u233? Ijifta fene ndimbal waft\u233? k\u233?nj\u250?n. ''W\u233?nde y\u233?nd t\u233? yaufi yam kufrotam a yaufiyam afoghare y\u233?n\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
T\u233?fene ndimbalfifi gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? fandagh k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?, Yur\u233?, gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? t\u233?ngwengo nde nayu fene f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? n\u233?kw k\u233?tam\u233? fene ndimbal tesenta Jerusalem, fene nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar mband tunak\u233?f. M\u233?inyotio kaka f\u250?tar ndimbal yu k\u233?s em tasalitaw\u233?t Jerusalem a fene \u225?r w\u233?i m\u233?nam\u233?n t\u233?fene yaufi yamm\u233?n a w\u233?i t\u233?fene akafene yaufiyamm\u233?n.
