Y\u233?mo ta kwawafenau, "Daniel, y\u233?nd y\u233?nan kw\u233?n\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t so k\u233?maraman mwighat a mat yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efogh f\u233?nef\u233?neyan f\u233?mo njam Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? y\u233?rnai, wafar\u233?gh si y\u233?ramay\u233?nd. A s\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd y\u233?na w\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i n\u233?maufrotan fe n\u233?mam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m merfifi Ng\u225?nj\u225?nefaf. N\u225?y\u225?reta merk\u233?r\u225?ye m\u233?n\u225?t f\u233?m so mat k\u225?y\u225?to fene gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?ghoene fifi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
490 yunj\u233?f t\u233? n\u225?ke enamndangi fene \u225?r\u233?t a fene nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar ndimbal tesenoe, m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tifongi n\u225?k rafar\u233?gh yam, m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i yafrotat \u225?nde yaufiyam so eyato m\u233?n\u225?t so yafrotat afer\u233?gh yam yaufiyamm\u233?n, m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i t\u233?nyawangi tuot mbark\u225?nd yam, m\u233?n\u225?t so tafrendangi gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?gh yam a ufroghm\u233?n si m\u233?n\u225?t so t\u233?fagharngi minde nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar sifay\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?m so mat n\u233?m a mat n\u233?ngay\u225?tota nden\u233? njam y\u233?n\u233? w\u225?faregh n\u225?k t\u233?ramangi m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i w\u233?ikor takayongi a ram\u233?gh w\u233?ikor tafngongi Jerusalem k\u233?t\u225?notio lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r o t\u233?gh kaf \u225?r efe y\u233?m waftaf\u233? \u225?r k\u233?t\u233? so em 434 yunj\u233?f so kor w\u233?i y\u233?rametat, m\u233?naye ende a moat, m\u233? t\u233?u t\u233?krat efogh k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
F\u233?yo 434 yunj\u233?f soram\u233? t\u233?ghkaf \u225?r so y\u233?smetat k\u233?rotio a n\u233?m\u233? \u225?mb yau so tafrangongi a lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r so kokayong\u233? endene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?ram so yironat ndimbal tesen a w\u225?wefnogh sifay\u233?. Kerekeran so y\u233?n\u233?m nu k\u233?f\u233?r, a m\u233?k a yane wawersogh yam so y\u233?m wafar\u233?gh n\u225?kan k\u233?t\u233? so m\u233?k m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye yam y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?notio kerkerfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
