\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Naikaita warsagh \u225?r so n\u233?kwam tifong\u233? a kuwanong\u233? a \u225?sm\u233?gh kufngend yambermata warsagh \u225?rf\u233?. F\u233?yo soram\u233? so kokayongi \u225?r s\u233?f, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r s\u233?f siya y\u233?m so taramangi k\u233?t\u225?n fronde efe t\u233?morw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233? m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r njam tawalindang\u233? naikaita warsagh \u225?r so tuktukam tifong\u233? a so t\u233?kratan k\u233?m\u233?gh tawafngong\u233? a k\u233?rotio yane t\u225?rf\u225?r tausen m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r. W\u233?nde yane klisa y\u233?nayan siya y\u233?m yau so teke y\u233?ng\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
"A t\u225?rf\u225?rofnar yunj\u233?f soram\u233? yamb\u233?rmata warsagh \u225?r so kangong\u233? a teketeke s\u233?f fiyaraf\u233? fronde nden\u233? yau y\u233?morm\u233?n mindeyo so y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon k\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m marataye okayogh yam s\u225?i y\u233?senat n\u225?ik\u225?ita warsagh \u225?r. W\u225?s\u233?mbogh \u225?r f\u233?fenjo k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?n so nuf\u233?indat y\u233?fefaf y\u233?n\u233? gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?ghoene fifi sof nufrote, w\u233?nde f\u225? yau so taremngong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo yamb\u233?rmata warsagh \u225?r so y\u233?n\u233?m a so t\u233?kmang\u233? yam ronjagh\u233?t taikrataye anaweghkaf ndimbal tesenoe a t\u233?nawangi. Mer \u225?sm\u233?gh fiyar\u233? m\u233?r\u233?n yau so f\u233?yotaro em s\u225?i kokayongi m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye m\u233?kan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
"Yamb\u233?rmata warsagh \u225?r so folen nden\u233? m\u233? emo so t\u233?karotang\u233?; yau emo so t\u233?kmbong\u233?. F\u225? so fronde k\u233?kmbong\u233? k\u233?t\u233? ndimbal kwayagh\u233? yuwon Israil tafnong\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t wirorgh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
Y\u233?mo so mwigh\u233? y\u233?farone m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i k\u233?nwanong\u233? muyaf\u233? m\u233?inyotio yane lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?rf\u233? a so kafeghangi yafrotat m\u233?r\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233? n\u225?ik\u225?ita warsagh \u225?rf\u233?. Y\u233?mo so t\u225?ramang\u233? yamr\u233?s awer\u233?gh\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t siya y\u233?ngwita yane k\u233?nj\u250?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh yam, w\u233?nde yane mwigh\u233? wafroghm\u233?n yam so nufrote.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? soram\u233?, y\u233?mo so tengong\u233? y\u225?njo mwigh\u233? nden\u225?ye arakaf t\u233?ndo mbandta a so tawerang\u233? t\u225?rf\u225?r ndimbal tesen. W\u233?nde fiyar\u233? wafar\u233?gh s\u233?nko \u225?r \u225?mb yum\u233?n y\u233?mo so t\u233?kmbong\u233? yane karogh yam a m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye us\u233?rmbogh t\u233?fngong\u233? w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Y\u233?mo so tanang\u233? yandio atnogh taikrataye awamb\u233?gh sifay\u233? w\u233?nde so m\u233? n\u225?ut\u225?ne a kuyang\u233? a yau so y\u233?ngfandat w\u233?ikor.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 20\~}
"F\u225? efe t\u233?remngote y\u225?faf y\u233?mo so yafarete mani kaf\u233?gh \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i kor y\u233?frendat warsagh \u225?roene kwayagh\u233?. W\u233?nde yane t\u233?njfie lim\u225?n\u233?ghan f\u225? \u233? k\u233?r so y\u233?m, yau n\u233?kwm\u233?n o m\u233?kan.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
"\u193?mb w\u233?i so y\u233?n\u233?m waftaf\u233? so y\u233?m krufr\u225?t yamofnar \u225?r efe yau kor n\u225?temnde warsagh \u225?rfene remnogh yamam\u233?. F\u225? so kaunotang\u233? njam nambio \u225?r\u233?mro kawanjetat a y\u233?ngwanangi warsagh \u225?r lim\u225?n\u233?gh m\u233?naye kembne wamnar\u233?ghe a kwankwane mwigh\u233? f\u225?ror\u233?ghe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 22\~}
Y\u225? soram\u233? ndimbal fiyar\u233? so tasenangi, y\u233?mofayo warsagh \u225?rta lim\u225?n\u233?gh ambum emo r\u233?ny\u233?ghyam yafrotam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 23\~}
Soram\u233? f\u250?tar yam njam yafrotam y\u233?mof\u233? y\u233?mo so t\u233?ngwafngon\u233? utar\u233?gh yam, a so karmbong\u233? a tanangi waft\u233? y\u233?maf\u233? n\u233?mbnar \u225?r m\u233?rnaf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 24\~}
Yau so gh\u233?k\u233?f ewafande f\u225? m\u233? so n\u233?nyawete d\u233?gw\u233?r mband sifayam\u233?. F\u233?yo y\u233?mo so efene y\u225?njo waitogh \u225?r\u233?t orom\u233?n rokar a mani ngonj\u233?l wem\u225?rm\u233?n nden\u233? yau yane fronde \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?ram stawafrotaw\u233?t. Y\u233?mo so kwankwane mwigh\u233? y\u233?farone s\u225?i y\u233?ngtarna t\u225?ik\u233?r awer\u233?gh sifay\u233?, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? yau so y\u233?m teke.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 25\~}
Y\u233?mo so y\u233?ngote y\u225?njo muy\u233? a m\u233?ghm\u233?gh y\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t warsagh \u225?r n\u225?ik\u225?ita ndimbal fiyar\u233? s\u233?faf\u233?. F\u233?yo warsagh \u225?r n\u225?ik\u225?ita y\u233?mo unogh ewafngoi minde s\u233?fe a muy\u233? k\u233?r ro fiyar\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t m\u233?kot w\u233?nde f\u225? yau so kokayong\u233?, m\u233?nam\u233?n mwigh\u233? so y\u233?faronat y\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 26\~}
Y\u225?njo m\u233?ngo \u225?r\u233?m so tifongi. Yane fiyar\u233? so esambunat, a t\u225?rf\u225?r so k\u233?rotio esmetat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 27\~}
Y\u233?ta n\u233?m\u233? so engronjat w\u233?nde f\u225?yo so n\u233?ngawas\u233?rmbotat, y\u233?n\u233? warsagh \u225?r so em kwankwane mwigh\u233? so n\u233?ngarsat k\u233?t\u233? \u225?umeng\u233?gh kitarafaf, so kufngoi s\u225?i n\u233?ngawindat. W\u233?nde n\u233?m\u233? yau \u225?mb f\u233?nataye so yafrotat, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u225?toghfaf so y\u233?m y\u225?njo kaf\u233?ghm\u233?n efghon.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 28\~}
"Warsagh \u225?r yamb\u233?rmata t\u225?f sofnangote m\u233?ngotuot ndimbal w\u233?maraf\u233?. N\u233?ndkfan f\u225? so afreng\u233?gh kufngong\u233? nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar r\u233?ny\u233?gh yam t\u233?fn\u225?rafefaf, yafrota minde was\u233?rmbogh soram\u233? so kufngong\u233? \u225?ligh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 29\~}
"F\u233?yo k\u233?t\u233? ufoghm\u233?n efghon f\u225? so korw\u233?i ambinotaro n\u225?ik\u225?ita t\u233?ngwanang\u233?, w\u233?nde s\u233?nonjo efogh y\u233?naoene fifi siya y\u233?m f\u233?nataye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 30\~}
M\u233?k bout s\u225?i em k\u233?tamam\u233?n mbormbor tambna arakaf t\u233?ndo mbandam so f\u233?rf\u233?rot yawindat, a f\u225? so k\u233?torng\u233? a n\u233?ngangota m\u233?ngotuot. W\u233?nde y\u233?mo so m\u233?nd\u233?gh tawafngong\u233? n\u233?kwe nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar r\u233?ny\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r \u225?r a fai so ewafrote f\u225? emofem mwighafnar yitam\u233?nd r\u233?ny\u233?gh yam.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 31\~}
Yane fiyaram so fiyar\u233? tanangi t\u225?ik\u233?r w\u225?wefnogh eny\u225?uw\u233?gh m\u233?ngo sifay\u233? yaghnat awanjar\u233?gh sifay\u233?, ekmbotat efoghm\u233?n gh\u233?ng\u233?n yam a y\u233?frendat \u225?mb ufarogh mbanmban \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u225?yan so y\u233?funat was\u233?rmbogh yam. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 32\~}
F\u225? m\u233? siero so narmbote a so erse f\u225? emofem y\u225?ghnat r\u233?ny\u233?gh yam. W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe mat em y\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n so em muyaro a y\u233?kenat f\u225?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 33\~}
"Kafet\u233? mwighaf\u233? lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?ram so ewarametat wawanjagh si t\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r\u233?t, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? watamegh t\u233?fn\u225?r so k\u233?r em f\u233?se a witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naifaye, o f\u225? so n\u225?k m\u233?ngot enyawetat o oroe ewarsat rokar. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 34\~}
T\u225?f y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?krat yam k\u233?nj\u250?n, n\u233?mbnar w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh so kufarng\u233? a t\u225?rf\u225?r efe kuf\u233?indat y\u233?fefaf yau so mwigh\u233? ong\u233?n so em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 35\~}
\u193?mb k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? \u225?r s\u225?i em so kuyangi k\u233?rtat k\u233?t\u225?n t\u233?krat yamfaf. Y\u233?n\u233? ende, f\u225? ewafrote tot\u233?r a eumb\u233?ne a tawafrotang f\u233?m\u233?ghf\u233?m\u233?ghofnar k\u233?t\u225?notio efogh kerkerfaf m\u233?nam\u233?n kaf\u233?ghm\u233?n efogh m\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 36\~}
"Warsagh \u225?rom so ewafrote y\u233?n\u233? s\u225?i y\u233?ngremngota, n\u233?ngawarmbota f\u225?ro a n\u233?ngamndeta s\u225?i y\u233?m ndimbalfifi engwainde m\u233?inyotio ng\u225?nj\u225?n, so yaufi so y\u233?mndete ng\u225?nj\u225?nafene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n. Y\u233?mo so m\u233?nde yifote, w\u233?nde k\u233?t\u225?notio n\u233?kw efogh s\u225?i kefong\u233?. F\u233?yo n\u233?m\u233? t\u233? mwigh\u233? t\u233? mwighaye t\u233?knam so sifay\u233? tanang\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 37\~}
Yane yau so y\u233?m utman\u233?gh y\u233?fene \u225?kiafene ng\u225?nj\u225?nfaf o y\u233?n\u233? ng\u225?nj\u225?ne amafam efe yuwetat, o \u225?rk\u233? ng\u225?nj\u225?ne t\u233?u, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u225? so narwarse nden\u233? f\u225? siy\u233?m ndimbalfifi ewainde f\u225? m\u233?inyotio. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 38\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ta s\u225?i y\u233?m, y\u233?mo so ew\u225?wefnote t\u225?ik\u233?r eny\u225?uw\u233?gh y\u233?n\u233? ng\u225?nj\u225?nafet yane y\u225?kif \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? mafina tamorw\u233?n a \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? klisaf\u233? tamorw\u233?n y\u225?faf gol, silf\u233?, merfifi w\u233?n k\u233?s em, a minde tuk\u233?n ram\u233?gh k\u233?s em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 39\~}
"Tawatnagh y\u233?n\u233? \u225?mb yum\u233?n ng\u225?nj\u225?nafene w\u225?ut\u225?r\u233?gh, y\u233?mo so tawafngong\u233? minde muyaf\u233? t\u225?ik\u233?r eny\u225?uw\u233?gh yu k\u233?s em. Y\u233?mo so eutemnde f\u225? emofem f\u225? efe namyotat y\u225?faf so ekafete f\u225? \u225?s\u225?fogh sifay\u233? waftafaf a ewafalota mband y\u233?fe nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?fene fai.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 40\~}
F\u233?yo kerker wighogh efoghfaf n\u225?ik\u225?ita warsagh \u225?rom m\u233?kot so tafngong\u233? yamb\u233?rmata warsagh \u225?r. Yamb\u233?rmata warsagh \u225?r so muyaf\u233? nurtote os r\u233?sagh rokar wawer\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r k\u233?s em, a s\u233?f n\u233?ifi bout. F\u225? m\u233? so muyaye n\u233?ngnyawete n\u233?ngofayote yu a y\u233?ngsambuna ndenanit nu k\u233?f\u233?ran y\u233?nau y\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 41\~}
F\u225? so k\u233?nyawang\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n ndimbal kwayagh\u233? yuot Israil, a t\u225?rf\u225?r ndimbal yu so nuitat, w\u233?nde Moab, Edom, a mer \u225?mb sifay\u233? Amoene so kengongi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 42\~}
Y\u233?mo so tawanang\u233? t\u225?rt\u225?f ndimbal yu w\u233?i Ijif f\u225?yo yau so kengong\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 43\~}
Y\u233?mo so muy\u233? tanang\u233? s\u225?i ewanjeta gol, silf\u233?, a Ijifene mani ngonj\u233?l, a Libiafene a Etiofiyane so em f\u225? yane \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?r.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 44\~}
"W\u233?nde ghanyam so t\u233?ramang\u233? f\u225? k\u233?tam\u233? werta a yamb\u233?rmata a y\u233?mo so y\u233?frende ndimbal n\u233?kw m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i ewas\u233?rmbota a engwalinde ambino t\u225?rt\u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 45\~}
F\u225? so k\u233?kmbong\u233? y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?ndk\u233?fan nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar mband tunak\u233?ffaf a arakaf a so eramete y\u225?njo warsagh \u225?r farai m\u233?ngo. W\u233?nde njam f\u225? k\u233?t\u233? m\u233? y\u233?m, yane efogh so s\u233?lngw\u233?le kefong\u233?, a \u225?rk\u233? \u225?rom yau so yautane.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 12
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Kerker efogh
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
K\u233?t\u233? y\u233?n\u233? efghon Maikol, minde tuk\u233?n waftaf\u233?! Efe yakai yambete f\u233?fene ndimbal yu, so kokayong\u233?. F\u233?yo k\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m t\u233?krat yam ndimbalfifi yau nden\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n t\u225?f mband njam nufrotam. W\u233?nde k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?n\u233? efghon m\u233?inyotio fene \u225?r endefene y\u233?tkw\u233?n ekai bukan so kunjarngi. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
T\u225?rf\u225?r \u225?r endefene fifi k\u233?rw\u233?n engk\u233?m a endyatotam\u233?nd so kanongi, \u225?mb so em tuot gh\u233?rsat a \u225?mb so em w\u225?iw\u225?iaf\u233? a ambino k\u233?rot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u225? efe em k\u225?fet\u233? mwighaf\u233? so n\u225?l\u225?l\u225?t ndenanit njafar kwamkwam kwayaghanit, a y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emofem \u225?r t\u225?rf\u225?r elimndat mbark\u225?nd gh\u233?rsafaf so n\u225?l\u225?l\u225?t ndenanit k\u233?nd tuot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
