\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo, Daniel n\u233?ngretay\u233?n a ewinjeyay\u233?n s\u243?mbio \u225?mb \u225?r tawakayarw\u233?n wanje t\u233?ndo kaka. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
\u193?mb \u225?rom y\u233?motai \u225?r tomb\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me umaneghkaf t\u233?morw\u233?n, efe t\u233?kayong\u233?rw\u233?n nu tuk\u233?n, "Nder\u233? teke so k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u233?n\u233? sunsunaf\u233? yam s\u225?i kawaindangi?"
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
\u193?r y\u233?n\u233? tomb\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me umaneghkaf efe takayong\u233?rw\u233?n nu tuk\u233?n, euyeyan s\u243?mbio ngagn\u233? njafarta a ambino kw\u233?rnare si norayai yanem\u233?n efe nakete tuot, korayau, "Y\u233?n\u233? so y\u233?m efogh kw\u233?fe efogh kw\u233?f s\u225?i em, a y\u233?n\u233? efogh kw\u233?f s\u225?i n\u233?ndk\u233?f yafrota. Njam nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar \u225?rfene wiror\u233?gh yam yiyota k\u233?t\u225?n kerkerot, m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? yam sofn\u233?natyanat."
