F\u233?m korayangi k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?fefaf\u233?tio, "Y\u233?nd f\u233?yotaro taikre nawanjetam m\u233?n\u225?t nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar efogh s\u225?i kawanindangi f\u233?yo m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndfem so et\u233?rnam t\u233?fene rais. Njam so safat yiy\u225?to, f\u233?yo m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ndfem f\u233?yotaro so tang\u233?rnyang\u233?m t\u233?rar\u233?gh kor w\u233?i? F\u233?yo y\u233?ndfem f\u233?yotaro so tuk\u233?n muy\u233? tawanong\u233?m, ewafrotam uny\u233?gh ufogh, a warauny\u233?gh k\u233?rt\u233? ufoghm\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t wauny\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?fe t\u233?fene r\u233?sagh t\u233?fn\u225?rat. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u233?ndfem t\u233?i et\u233?rnam fifiofnar mbwem\u233?n wanjmeng\u233?ghkaf njamke k\u233?t\u233? tuk\u233?n faian. Y\u233?ndfem y\u233?ronjam \u225?mb \u225?r yauyau \u225?mbiro sandolm\u233?n fai, a merero r\u233?sagh yane nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? faiofnar \u225?s\u225?fogh \u225?r."
