Yur\u233?, Israilm\u233?n Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, t\u233? norayam, "Y\u233?nd yau so kwawalindang\u233? y\u233?fene yaufi yamm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
A f\u233?yo mband so nasambnete, a m\u233?inyotio k\u233?t\u233? mbandan so em m\u233?n\u225?yan ndimbal mwigh\u233? k\u233?rtayan. M\u233?inyotio yu tautau so em asambneng\u233?ghan; so nokayote a nuite ndenanit Nail wanje. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Efogh y\u233?na y\u233?n\u233?m njam y\u233?ndo so tafrotang\u233?n efogh ngeworng\u233? t\u225?f m\u233?f efoghe a mband t\u233?nmafarng\u233? kw\u233?fitam t\u225?f efogh. Y\u233?nd, Waft\u233?k\u233?r ro Yur\u233?, sw\u233?m norayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Y\u233?ndo so tengon f\u233?fene t\u233?m\u233?nd k\u233?t\u225?n k\u233?r t\u233?mndot a ewengotan f\u233?fene \u225?uw\u233?gh wagh m\u233?n\u225?t ndimbal k\u233?rtaf\u233? yeyot. Y\u233?ndo so tawanjar\u233?n f\u233?fene s\u233?nko \u225?r a ewawotan s\u233?njt\u233? s\u225?l\u225?me, a f\u233?m so em ndenanit afaf em gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisayan m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?fene m\u233? \u225?mbirofifi ambumm\u233?n. Y\u233?n\u233? efogh so y\u233?m ghaft\u233? k\u233?t\u225?notio y\u225?toghfaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
"Efogh siy\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?m njam y\u233?ndo so y\u233?nmafaretan ndimbal k\u233?rt\u233? yam nbandot, \u225?r so em siogh, w\u233?nde yau m\u233?n\u225?t flawat, f\u225? so em nendat nu n\u233?net, w\u233?nde yau nuot. F\u225? so em siogh a m\u233?nde m\u233?n\u225?t siot k\u233?tam\u233? Yurata. Y\u233?nd, Waft\u233?k\u233?r ro Yur\u233? t\u233? korayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
