Y\u233?n\u233? efghon t\u233?u y\u233?m mulmulaf\u233? tot\u233?r \u225?r a amaf so noslafote m\u233?nam\u233?n nuofnarm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
