Y\u233?ndo t\u233?fandan Yur\u233? ttakai n\u233?mbnar m\u233?ngofaf. Y\u233?mon y\u233?nramang si: "Tawirorngi w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngoene mwighaf\u233? s\u233?ras\u233?r minde m\u233?n\u225?t t\u233?fen so kasambnetangi. Erafnati y\u233?n\u233? ambino a m\u233?n\u225?t so nuitat k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?rfene s\u233?nkofaf. Y\u233?ndo so esmetan \u225?mb \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?yan m\u233?kan. Yau efe \u225?mb so nalait\u233? yau \u225?mbiro so kunjarng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Njam t\u233? y\u233?mofen etanat y\u233?fenjo end yuot k\u233?t\u225?n mbandot k\u233?rm\u233?n, y\u233?ndo so taweran f\u225?. Njam t\u233? f\u225? narmbotat k\u233?t\u225?n njafarot, y\u233?ndo so tanwewor\u233?n f\u225? yuot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Njam f\u225? katnongi k\u233?t\u233? mband tunak\u233?f Kemol tuk\u233?n, y\u233?ndo so eronjam a tawinjon f\u225?. Njam f\u225? natnotat m\u233?nam\u233?n tanem\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? ararkaf mbanmbanan, y\u233?ndo so t\u233?mndan arakaf w\u233?r\u225?r m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fe rargh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Njam f\u225? m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?ram tangw\u225?nango tangiy\u225?tongi d\u225?biot, y\u233?ndo so tawafaretang\u233?n f\u225? m\u233?n\u225?t so t\u225?kmangi k\u233?ran. Y\u233?nd w\u233?m mwigh\u233? freng\u233?ghkaf m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fer wirorgh\u233?t, yau m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?fe w\u225?ut\u225?rgh\u233?t."
