F\u233?mo t\u233? tawotrote amaf k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?fenjo freng\u233?ghaf\u233? m\u233?ngota a tuot tafit\u233?rne y\u233?fene ambum y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?inyotio Ng\u225?nj\u225?nam ewaram y\u233?fe. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
Kokai a kuwano; k\u233?t\u233? siy\u233?m yau wajar\u233?gh y\u233?na kor w\u233?i. Fene yaufiyam t\u233? y\u233?nman y\u233?n\u233? sifay\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n k\u233?rtat.
