"W\u233?nde y\u233?ndo so taumendang\u233?n f\u233?m m\u233?rne, Israilm\u233?n \u225?r m\u233?inyotio f\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rk\u233? naf\u225?ngongi. Y\u233?ndo so tanwanan f\u233?m m\u233?rne ndenanit sif n\u233?nangote k\u233?t\u225?n k\u233?naghfaf. Nden\u233? yusyusat mband sif ofayoghare, fene mband so ambinotar kor w\u233?i ofayoghare y\u233?m \u225?r t\u225?rf\u225?re."
