K\u225?y\u225?rangi, f\u233?m Israilm\u233?n n\u225?k \u225?r! F\u233?mofem so mwigh\u233? yafrotati m\u233?n\u225?t so y\u233?fandati n\u225?k, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
w\u233?nde f\u233?mofem y\u233?kenat n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m mer a yuwetat n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m yaufi. F\u233?mofem ewatonat tane gh\u233?rs\u233? \u225?r a ef\u233?rnat fifi y\u233?fene sotta. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?t\u233?, f\u233?mofem enetat tane \u225?rfene fifi, ewatonat y\u233?fene njar, a er\u225?fnat y\u233?fene sot. F\u233?mofem enfetat f\u225? nden\u233? w\u233?r\u225?r k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?sm\u233?n sinot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Efogh y\u233?n\u233?m njam f\u233?m so nendat k\u233?t\u225?n Yurafaf, w\u233?nde yau y\u233?mo so tawawangong\u233? f\u233?fe. Y\u233?mo yau so n\u225?y\u225?rete f\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh si, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?mofem t\u233? tawafrotat yaufi.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? siy\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? Yur\u233? noraye" "F\u233?m uny\u233?gh si waitogh \u225?r elimndat tane \u225?r yaufie! F\u233?m m\u233?tarm\u233?n uny\u233?ghofnar si noraye y\u233?feyot emofem k\u233?maramangi njamke feyot, w\u233?nde f\u233?mo tuyafo m\u233?k y\u233?fefaf emofem k\u233?nkenangi manjargh\u233?t f\u233?m. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
"S\u233?nonjo s\u233?mb\u225?r so kamnang\u233? tawarendang\u233? f\u233?m, enfete m\u233?inyotio f\u233?fene gh\u233?k\u233?f waing\u233?gh. Kw\u233?fitam so tawafarng\u233? f\u233?m, t\u233?kmang\u233? k\u233?mbogh k\u233?t\u225?n f\u233?fene emar\u233?gh sifaf. Efogh so nafrende so waitogh \u225?r f\u233?feyot, a f\u233?fene efogh so y\u233?n\u233?m k\u233?t\u225?n y\u225?toghfaf." {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?m fandagh \u225?r so kakmangi w\u225?iw\u225?ian, a f\u233?m waufrogh \u225?r so em yaufiyan. A f\u233?mofem so ewafnat f\u233?fene s\u225?f m\u233?nam\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? siy\u233?m yau uwangogh k\u233?tam\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?neta.
