W\u233?nde nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? tayot, Yuram wafote y\u233?nd y\u225?njo mb\u233?rmb\u233?re a waftaye, a waramete ta mwigh\u233? n\u225?km\u233?n a si m\u233?n\u225?t siot Israil \u225?r\u233?t n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?fene yaufi em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Tafaf k\u225?y\u225?rangi, f\u233?m Israilm\u233?n lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r. F\u233?mofem y\u233?kenat n\u225?k a es\u233?nat m\u233?inyotio y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m mbark\u225?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?mo siy\u233?m Jerusalemene t\u233?fen y\u233?ramete k\u233?t\u233? ng\u233?ndan a k\u233?rtayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Ndimbal tesen n\u225?kan y\u225?njete m\u233?n\u225?t kembnat, gh\u233?ng\u233?n w\u225?rogh s\u233?nko \u225?r\u233?m y\u233?ngotat n\u225?k m\u233?n\u225?t fayot, si waitogh \u225?r\u233?m erametat y\u233?fenjo ufroghm\u233?n yam m\u233?n\u225?t maniot a f\u225? m\u233?inyotio nawarsat nden\u233? Yur\u233? siy\u233?m k\u233?t\u233? y\u233?fefaf. F\u225? norayat, "Yau s\u233?m\u233?gh so y\u233?n\u233?m y\u233?nan t\u233?fefaf. Yur\u233? siy\u233?m t\u233?fefaf."
