F\u225? efe em njang\u233?n so kunjarngi taikrataye, f\u225? efe tam d\u225?bi so kamndagni sotaf\u233? yu. F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo, Yuram, so enwanjetan k\u233?tam\u233? Jerusalemta nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?fene lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?r mbanjat."
