W\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? yu yau mat em n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?m Yurane mwigh\u233?. F\u225? yau mat em nden\u233? f\u225? stam kaumendat m\u233?rne m\u233?n\u225?t awafergh\u233?t nden\u233? s\u225?fot ende rais siy\u233?m y\u233?n\u233?rsat m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u233?m waferghan.
