Nden\u233? noraye tane Yur\u233? Ng\u225?nj\u225?n: "Tang\u233?m a ewarawenati tane sif \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? erametat ngiot a n\u233?f\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
Manie emofem ewanay\u233?nd sif y\u233?mofem tanafetaw\u233?t t\u233?krat amwamb\u233?ghofnar, maniot t\u233?rar\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r norayay\u233?nd, yuyotam Yur\u233?! S\u233?nonjo y\u233?nd w\u233?m wem\u225?r yau sif lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?rafene t\u233?morw\u233?n gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? y\u233?feyot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Nden\u233?yameyo y\u233?nd yau so w\u233?m gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisaf\u233? y\u233?n\u233? yu \u225?rfefaf, norayai Yur\u233?. "Y\u233?ndo so t\u225?ng\u233?ghmiyon y\u233?fenjo ng\u225?ngatio nguyangi a k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?fene warsagh \u225?rfene ng\u225?ngat. Y\u233?mofem so tengongi mband fanfne sifayat, a y\u233?ndo yau so tawanjar\u233?n f\u225?."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo tawarawenan sif a m\u233?nde y\u233?ta kw\u233?m s\u225?i tasmetaw\u233?n mwigh\u233? k\u233?rtaf\u233? sif. F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo ewaneyay\u233?n sif lim\u225?n\u233?gh \u225?rfene w\u233?tu a \u225?mb \u225?roe y\u233?tkw\u233?n yaramay\u233?n m\u233?ndef\u233? a \u225?mb \u225?roe m\u233?rne. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?ndo tawewetaw\u233?n y\u233?fene nambio yaufi sif wanjeng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r \u225?mbiro gh\u233?rareyan t\u225?f. W\u233?nde y\u233?nd n\u233?kwaf\u233? n\u233?namndan y\u233?n\u233? sifafefaf, a y\u233?mofem t\u233?krate kw\u233?rametat y\u233?nd w\u233?i. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo emnday\u233?n, "Y\u233?nd yau so w\u233?m f\u233?fene sif wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?r ndenayu. Njam f\u233?m k\u233?r em, so f\u233?t\u233? k\u233?r em. Njam f\u233?m k\u233?rotio esmetat, so f\u233?t\u233? k\u233?rotio esmetat. A taumyo f\u225? efe kafrangongi kawifongi f\u225?rof\u225?ro!" {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo yanay\u233?n tane w\u233?ti y\u233?tkw\u233?n y\u233?m m\u233?ndef\u233? a y\u233?nfay\u233?n s\u243?mbioyot, yuyafotam\u233?n nden\u233? y\u233?ndo t\u233? yangoy\u233?n \u225?rny\u233?gh yam \u225?rk\u233? yafrotam\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233? m\u233?inyotio ndimbal yu k\u233?s em. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? fiyomorm\u233?n yiy\u225?tong\u233?rm\u233?n tane arn\u233?gh yam y\u233?maf\u233?. Y\u233?n\u233? sif emo t\u233?krat t\u225?y\u225?retau y\u233?mo kw\u233?fandau y\u233?nd, a f\u225? mat namnday\u233?nd nden\u233? Yur\u233? korayau tane wafrogh yam k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
A y\u233?ndo emnday\u233?n f\u225?, "Njam f\u233?m m\u233?nde em, f\u225? kwaramangi, nder\u233?m\u233?n\u233? tayot y\u233?m, njenamb tane y\u233?m m\u233? y\u233?natro njam f\u233?m m\u233?nde em." F\u233?yo y\u233?mofem waf\u233?gh ewafngoy\u233?nd tane fai so silf\u233? mani mbwe.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?yo Yuram w\u233?mndai y\u233?nd, "Tungwai k\u233?t\u225?n ng\u233?nd sin wafrogh \u225?roefaf y\u233?n\u233? mer s\u225?fot mani y\u233?tkw\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?nd warmbongi! F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo engwanay\u233?n 30 toya mani mbwe a engwitam\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?n\u233? \u225?roefaf emo ng\u233?ndm\u233?nn rokar tawafrotau Yurane w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo y\u233?ngwanay\u233?n \u225?mb w\u233?tu, y\u233?mndetat yane k\u233?nj\u250?n a y\u233?nfay\u233?n s\u243?mbioyot, yuyafotam nden\u233? \u225?mbiro \u225?rk\u233? tamorw\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233? Juda a Israil t\u233? nirory\u233?ng.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
F\u233?yo Yuram w\u233?mndai y\u233?nd, nguwano w\u233?ikor a kembne y\u233?n\u233? fifiofnar sif wanjeng\u233?gh \u225?roene sifayan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? waufarogh yamm\u233?n ndern\u225?ye so taraman y\u233?n\u233? ndimbal yuoe y\u233?n\u233? sif wanjeng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?roe emo yau siya ewarawena f\u225? efe k\u233?r em, yau s\u225?i ewanjeta tot\u233?r \u225?r, yau s\u225?i mer eyatotat k\u225?l \u225?r, yau emanjna ndur\u233?m \u225?r, w\u233?nde y\u233?n\u233? sif wanjeng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?ram so m\u233?inyotio sifafene fenj\u233?n a engtirna y\u233?fene ng\u225?ng\u233? sot.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
N\u233?m\u233? ye yamam y\u225?njete y\u233?n\u233? kor fifiofnar sif wanjengh t\u233?fn\u225?r emo efrangote sif! Witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? naifayam so tanfang\u233? yane ndangw\u233?s a takuinyang\u233? yane tamb\u233?n gh\u233?k\u233?f. Yane ng\u225?ng\u233? so k\u233?namndang\u233? fifiofnar, a yane tamb\u233?n gh\u233?k\u233?f ambino kamndangi kw\u233?fkw\u233?f."
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 12
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Soram\u233? yuwon wanjar\u233?gh y\u233?fe Israil \u225?r\u233?t
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? si siy\u233?m y\u233?fene Israil \u225?rfene ambino watemb\u233?ghm\u233?n y\u233?nmorm\u233?n k\u233?tam\u233? Yurata: "Y\u233?n\u233? si siy\u233?m Yurata, emo marat ey\u225?totam njafar, yeitam mbandoene wer\u233?ghm\u233?n t\u233?f\u233?n, a y\u233?finai \u225?roene mb\u233?rmb\u233?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?ndo so yafrotan Jerusalem ndenanit w\u233?ri nu so tawafrotang\u233? kaka nidmbal yu tik\u233?f kanefangi t\u225?f njam ewafretat y\u233?fene fiyar\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i tawarendangi Jerusalme a Juda. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?ndo so tiy\u225?ton Jerusalem wimn\u225?ng\u233?ghofnar w\u233?m. M\u233?inyotio ndimbal yu so n\u233?naumendat ya s\u233?nan\u233?gh\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ta tufongi wim\u225?ng\u233?gh\u233?t, w\u233?nde f\u225?yo so nawas\u233?rmnotat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Yur\u233? noraye, "Y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?ndo so tameindang\u233?n m\u233?inyotio os so tik\u233?f nanefetat a m\u233?inyotio wawer\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r muyafnar kamndangi. Y\u233?ndo so efandan Judam\u233?n \u225?r, w\u233?nde y\u233?ndo so gh\u233?k\u233?f kw\u233?fkw\u233?f tayoton y\u233?fene m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?rafene m\u233?inyotio os. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
A \u225?r t\u233?f\u233?n m\u233?r\u233?n Judam\u233?n so norayat f\u225?rof\u225?ro, Jerusalemm\u233?n \u225?r\u233?m t\u233? yinjongi muy\u233? njafam\u233?n fiyarafene Yurata, y\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n.'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon y\u233?ndo so t\u225?y\u225?ton Judam\u233?n \u225?r t\u233?f\u233?n m\u233?r\u233?n ndenanit f\u233?s kak\u233? freng\u233?ghkaf nden\u233? f\u233?s kar\u233?f tar\u233?tar\u233? nak\u233?rne o ndenanit tosin k\u225?r naneta y\u233?nam\u233? s\u233?f rais mbwefaf. Y\u233?mofem so ewak\u233?rnat m\u233?inyotio kaka ndimbal yu tamb\u233?nta a fatarata, t\u225?f y\u233?fe Jerusalemm\u233?n \u225?r so emor f\u225? merro.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
"Yurane so tawaramang\u233? s\u225?i waing\u233?gh muy\u233? kawandangi m\u233?inyotio Juda \u225?r\u233?t fronde, soram\u233? Jerusalem\u233?t m\u233?n\u225?t Jerusalemm\u233?n \u225?r a tik\u233?f fandaghaf\u233? \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n Deifidene yau so eut\u233?mndat ndimbale a yau kar \u225?mb Judam\u233?n \u225?r. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon Yuram so tawamarotang\u233? Jerusalem \u225?r. Muyafnar \u225?r y\u233?fene k\u233?nj\u250?n so em minde muyaf\u233? nden\u233? warsagh \u225?r Deifid k\u233?s t\u233?morw\u233?n a tik\u233?f fandaghaf\u233? \u225?kiambum m\u233?r\u233?n so em ndenanit Ng\u225?nj\u225?n, ndenanit Yurane njafar si r\u233?sagh \u225?r efe y\u233?ng\u233?m frondeyo y\u233?feta! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
M\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon y\u233?ndo so tafngon s\u225?i ewironan m\u233?inyotio ndimbal yu k\u233?s em \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? en\u233?m Jerusalem s\u233?nan\u233?gh\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?ndo so tasur\u233?n gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? mb\u233?rmb\u233?r a Ng\u225?nj\u225?naf\u233? oray\u233?gh y\u233?fenem\u233?n Deifidene m\u233?r\u233?nm\u233?n a y\u233?fenem\u233?n Jerusalem \u225?rfenem\u233?n. F\u225? so n\u233?nretat tafaf efe y\u233?mofem t\u233? y\u233?kunyay\u233?nd a yey\u233? yarametat ndenanit y\u233?naro ambum k\u225?r t\u233?morw\u233?n. F\u225? so nendat m\u225?m\u233?gh\u233?raye y\u225?yot fronde s\u233?nko ambumoe efe k\u233?r t\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
Ye a gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? Jerusalem k\u233?nj\u250?n y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon so y\u233?m ndenanit ndimbal ye y\u225?yot Edad-rimon ewor\u233?gh sifayafaf.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
"M\u233?inyotio Israil \u225?r so nendat, \u225?r t\u233?f\u233?n m\u233?r\u233?nero y\u233?fembiaye, a y\u233?maf\u233? y\u233?fenjar\u233?f f\u225?logh k\u233?tam\u233? y\u233?fene amafafeta. Deifidene \u225?r t\u233?f\u233?n m\u233?r\u233?n so nendat f\u225?ro, a so w\u233?i nden\u233?yameyo Natanene \u225?r t\u233?fen m\u233?r\u233?n, {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Lefiene \u225?r t\u233?f\u233?n a Simeiene \u225?r t\u233?f\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
\u193?mb Judam\u233?n \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n efe t\u233? nunjary\u233?nd so ye nendat f\u233?natayero a y\u233?fenjar\u233?f so kafalongi y\u233?fenjo amafta.
