\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?r\u233?r nu umbar\u233?ghm\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon w\u233?r\u233?r nu so t\u233?saw\u233?rngi m\u233?n\u225?t Deifidene lim\u225?n\u233?gh siya y\u233?m a y\u233?feyot Jerusalem \u225?r\u233?t, y\u233?n\u233? nu m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i eumb\u233?na f\u225? k\u233?tam\u233? m\u233?inyotio y\u233?fene yaufiyamta a nj\u250?nnj\u250?nta.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Njafarm\u233?n fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye, "A y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon y\u233?ndo so engsenan mewang w\u225?wefnogh yam m\u233?inyotio mbandan m\u233?n\u225?t mewangafene y\u233?tkw\u233?n so y\u233?ngmawalinde. Y\u233?ndo so tawit\u233?rmbon k\u233?tam\u233? mbandta uny\u233?gh mat y\u225?togh \u225?r a nj\u250?nj\u250?n k\u233?r ro mb\u233?rmb\u233?r \u225?rk\u233? enmorm\u233?n y\u233?maf\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Njam \u225?rk\u233? \u225?r m\u233?njt\u233? y\u233?ng\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t ufroghm\u233?n si s\u225?i n\u233?ngoraya, yankp y\u225?refaf\u233?m a yatmafem so t\u233?mndend, f\u233?m so k\u233?r n\u233?m, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?m t\u233? koray\u233? ufroghm\u233?n si uny\u233?gh Yurane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan. A njam f\u225? ufroghm\u233?n si noraye, y\u225?njo y\u225?ref\u233? a y\u225?tm\u233? so t\u233?kuiny\u233?nd naifaye.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
"Y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon \u225?r so em w\u225?iw\u225?i s\u225?i nafayotat m\u233? ram\u233?gh \u225?rk\u233? y\u233?morm\u233?n ufroghm\u233?n sifaf. Efe yau so aninjo nuinde s\u225?i y\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r m\u233?n\u225?yan s\u225?i yawo Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?rfene s\u225?l\u225?me. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u225? so noraye, 'Y\u233?nd yau w\u233?m Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh \u225?r. Y\u233?nd w\u233?m ndau t\u233?fn\u225?rro. Y\u233?ndo y\u233?n\u233?rnyay\u233?n ndau \u225?s\u225?fogh njam b\u233?rkar\u225?r kw\u233?nmorw\u233?n. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
A njam \u225?mb \u225?r kamotang\u233?, 'W\u233?t mbor y\u233?n\u233? em fene w\u233?fan? F\u225? so karayang\u233?, y\u233?nd kal wafrogtam\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? tane f\u250?tarene m\u233?ngon!'
