Njafarm\u233?n fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye, "Kano, o witmaf\u233? s\u233?nt\u233? n\u225?if\u233?, y\u233?fe s\u233?nan\u233?gh\u233?t tane sif wanjeng\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r efe y\u233?m tane f\u250?tar. Yur\u233? noraye, "T\u233?tar\u233?m sif lim\u225?n\u233?gh t\u233?fn\u225?r, a sif so kofarnangi y\u233?nd so kawengon tot\u233?r sif k\u233?s em y\u233?fe s\u233?nan\u233?gh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
S\u243?mbio a nambiom\u233?n tausen \u225?r mbandan so tanfan a so k\u233?r em. W\u233?nde \u225?mbiro a yambiom\u233?n taus\u233?n so kafrongongi mbandan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
Y\u233?ndo so en\u233?mnjan y\u233?n\u233? m\u233?r\u233?n f\u233?s k\u233?nj\u250?m\u233? a ty\u225?ton f\u233?m\u233?ghf\u233?m\u233?ghofnar, y\u233?ndo so kor efanan nden\u233? silf\u233? k\u233?s em a f\u233?njf\u233?njofnar t\u225?y\u225?ton nden\u233? gol k\u233?s em. F\u225? so nutmant tane y\u233?tkw\u233?nan, a y\u233?ndo so ewawangotan y\u233?fe. Y\u233?nd so noyayan, y\u233?n\u233? fem tane \u225?r, a f\u225? so norayat, Yur\u233? siy\u233?m t\u233?fene Ng\u225?nj\u225?n."
