N\u233?retat, m\u233?nam\u233?n Yurane efogh y\u233?n\u233?m njam f\u233?fene \u225?s\u225?fogh sifay\u233? so y\u233?ngwasnende fene s\u225?fanyo! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
Y\u233?ndo so eumendan m\u233?inyotio ndimbal yu m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i n\u225?smetat y\u233?maf\u233? Jerusalen. Ndimbal tesen so tanangi, m\u233?ngo mam\u233?gh\u233?raye ersat, a amaf engrogh\u233?t. \u193?mb afrengogh \u225?r m\u233?r\u233?n so enyawetat n\u225?k m\u233?ngot a \u225?mb so nafrangotat ndimbal tesen was\u233?mbogh sifayam\u233?.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
F\u233?yo Yur\u233? so nguwanong\u233? ng\u233?torng\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i nasmetat y\u233?n\u233? efogh k\u233?s n\u233?nawainday\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon yane kafkaf so kokayongi Olif Mband tunk\u233?fan, Jerusalemm\u233?n w\u233?rta. A Olif Mband tunak\u233?f so kar\u233?f nufrote, tafrotang\u233? marat ewor\u233?gh y\u233?kw n\u233?n\u233?rsa k\u233?tam\u233? w\u233?r tamb\u233?n k\u233?t\u225?n mbormbor tamb\u233?n mbarmbar mband tunak\u233?f so kimndang\u233? nden\u225?ye yamb\u233?rmata o \u225?mb mbarmbar nden\u225?ye n\u225?ik\u225?ita. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
F\u233?m so kit\u233?rmbongi y\u233?n\u233? ewor\u233?gh y\u233?kwta, m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?n\u233? so k\u233?fermang\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n Ajal. N\u233?m\u233?w\u233?t, f\u233?m so kit\u233?rmbongi nden\u233? y\u233?nau nit\u233?rmboy\u233?nd t\u225?f sokrere njam y\u233?morm\u233? y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon njam Ujaia warsagh \u225?r t\u233?morw\u233?n Judan. F\u233?yo Yur\u233? tane Ng\u225?nj\u225?n so y\u233?n\u233?m, a y\u233?maf\u233? m\u233?inyotio yane nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar \u225?r k\u233?s em.
