W\u233?nde k\u233?t\u233? m\u233? so y\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? efghon! M\u233? Yuraro mat y\u233?m ndern\u225?ye y\u233?n\u233? so nufrote. K\u233?t\u233? so ere m\u233?inyo efogh a s\u233?mb\u225?r, m\u233?nam\u233?n f\u233?r\u233?gh efoghf\u233?nef\u233?nan k\u233?t\u233? m\u233? so y\u233?m kwayagh\u233?.
