Y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon gh\u233?rs\u233? ram\u233?ghm\u233?n nu so y\u233?n\u233?frone k\u233?tam\u233? Jerusalemta \u225?mb kafe k\u233?t\u225?n k\u233?r arakafot a \u225?mb kafe k\u233?t\u225?n Mediterenia Arakaf f\u225? nden\u233? m\u233? y\u233?frone efogh yuwon a saian.
