A Yur\u233? so y\u233?m warsagh \u225?r m\u233?inyotio mbandan. Y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon k\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m \u225?mbiro Yur\u233? yane y\u233?tkw\u233?nanro w\u225?wefnogh yafrotat.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
M\u233?inyotio mbandan k\u233?tam\u233? Geba, yamb\u233?rmata Juda tamb\u233?n, k\u233?t\u225?n Rimon, Jerusalemm\u233?n naikaita, so y\u233?n\u233?m midne ndimbal fanfne yu. W\u233?nde Jerusalem so kuyong\u233? tuk\u233?t y\u225?njo t\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r sifayan a so fifay\u233? tawamong\u233? m\u233?inyotio k\u233?tam\u233? Benjamin s\u233?safneta k\u233?t\u225?n t\u225?nd\u225?w\u225?r s\u233?safne sifayafaf, f\u233?yo k\u233?tam\u233? k\u233?t\u225?n kw\u233?ndkw\u233?ndoene s\u233?safnefaf a k\u233?tam\u233? Ananelene f\u225?w\u225?ta k\u233?t\u225?n warsagh \u225?rfene wain tum\u225?ng\u233?ghfaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
A Jerusalem so kafong\u233? yau so yas\u233?rmbotat soram\u233?, yau w\u233?ikor so tafalngongi a tirorngi.
