F\u233?yo Yuram so y\u233?ngwafarete k\u233?rt\u233? yam y\u233?fefaf ndimbal yu k\u233?s em efe n\u225?smetat Jerusalemaf\u233?. Y\u233?fene \u225?r so kamndangi k\u233?r \u225?rnit eyota, y\u233?fene fifi so n\u233?ngorndat. Y\u233?fene gh\u233?k\u233?f yekwan so nengorndat gh\u233?k\u233?f, a y\u233?fene kank\u233? so n\u233?ngorndat y\u233?fene s\u233?nf\u233?neyan. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon f\u225? so em minde f\u233?rf\u233?ran so esmete Yuram tik\u233?f \u225?nef\u233?ghe. Y\u233?mofem so ewasmetat y\u233?fe f\u250?tarfene ng\u225?ng\u233? w\u233?ikor \u225?mb ng\u225?ng\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
Juda w\u233?i so n\u225?smetat k\u233?t\u233? Jerusalemm\u233?n mani ngonj\u233?l m\u233?inyotio kaka f\u250?tar ndimbal yuafene so kw\u233?rnare ersat t\u225?rf\u225?rfifi go a silf\u233? a mer s\u225?f salme. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? yamamyo so esmete os tik\u233?f t\u225?ik\u233?r \u225?r, kemol, ndonki a m\u233?inyotio \u225?mb w\u233?r\u225?r k\u233?s em m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?rafene m\u233?ngo \u225?ram\u233?h sifayam\u233?.
