Wifoghan, Jerusalemaf\u233? m\u233?k t\u233?fn\u225?r efe nafranoy\u233?nd k\u233?rt\u233? yaman so eng\u233?m ngarmbongi k\u233?t\u225?n Jerusalem m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i y\u225?wefnoghtat warsagh \u225?roe njafarm\u233?n fiyarafene Yurai, a s\u233?kis\u233?kim\u233?n t\u233?m\u233?nd s\u225?i ewafrotati. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
\u193?rk\u233? ndimbal yu y\u233?n\u233? mband maratan njam kawatnang\u233? m\u233?n\u225?t yau s\u225?i y\u233?n\u233?m Jerusalem\u233?t warsagh \u225?roe w\u225?wefnogh\u233?t, njafarm\u233?n fiyarafene yuratayau so n\u233?nanfamnde nu. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
Njam Ijifm\u233?n \u225?r nakenat yau s\u225?i eng\u233?m y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?m\u233?ndot, Yuram so t\u225?kmang\u233? t\u233?kratan y\u233?n\u233? k\u233?rt\u233? yameyot w\u233?i \u225?rk\u233?m\u233?n\u233? y\u233?mo engeyafaretai k\u233?t\u225?n \u225?mb ndimbal yu k\u233?s em efe nakenay\u233?nd \u225?ligh\u233?t. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 19\~}
Ijif a \u225?mb ndimbal yu k\u233?s em so m\u233?inyotio t\u225?kmang\u233? t\u233?kratan t\u225?f njam ayu eyota m\u233?n\u225?t s\u233?kis\u233?kim\u233?n t\u233?m\u233?nd wafrogh\u233?t.
