Y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?fon so osafene \u225?s\u225?fogh belbelam\u233? ekai y\u233?n\u233? si: Nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar aem Yurai. A njamke f\u233?sm\u233?n sin Yurane w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo k\u233?nj\u250?n so em auteman\u233?ghaf\u233? njam beisin \u225?s\u225?foghan em gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233? t\u233?ndofaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 21\~}
Merero, m\u233?inyotio njamke f\u233?sm\u233?n si k\u233?t\u233? Jerusalemm\u233?n a Judan so em nj\u250?nnj\u250?nofnar njafarm\u233?n Yurafaf. M\u233?inyotio efe s\u225?i en\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?t w\u225?wefnogh\u233?t so m\u233? yuwek em \u225?rk\u233? sinan t\u233?u nu f\u233?se eneghat y\u233?fendio gh\u233?ng\u233?n. A y\u233?n\u233? efghon k\u233?t\u233? yau so em y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emofem rokar maniot so et\u233?rnat njafarm\u233?n fiyarafene Yuraye w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo.
