Njafar Fiyarafene Yur\u233? y\u233?mota, "M\u233?njt\u233? aem, yamnendati Ng\u225?nj\u225?n s\u225?i y\u233?m gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? f\u233?fefaf! W\u233?nde f\u233?mo njam y\u233?n\u233?rsa nden\u233? s\u225?fot gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh, n\u233?mam\u233?n f\u225? so k\u233?mauyafong\u233? fene m\u233?ndef\u233? sem m\u233?inyotio?"
