Njafar Fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye, "Ndenaye nemnan \u225?mb \u225?rofem so emnat w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngo s\u233?safne m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?n\u233? fifiofnar gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh yau so gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh\u233?t y\u233?m! Y\u233?nd yau f\u233?fefaf klisaf\u233? w\u233?m a y\u233?ndon yau so eumyotan f\u233?fene gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
W\u233?nde tane y\u233?tkw\u233?n siy\u233?m yut\u233?mndat \u225?mb yu \u225?r\u233?m k\u233?tam\u233? akw k\u233?t\u225?n s\u233?m. M\u233?inyotio mband maratam\u233? y\u233?mofem m\u233?ndef\u233? gh\u233?ng\u233?n warametat a f\u233?w\u233?nf\u233?w\u233?nofnar gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh tane y\u233?tkw\u233?n utman\u233?gh\u233?t. Tane y\u233?tkw\u233?n siy\u233?m ndimbal m\u233?inyotio mband maratan."
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?m n\u233?m\u233? njafar fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye.
