"W\u233?nde f\u233?mofem yau ut\u233?mndati f\u233?fenjo wafrogh yaman. M\u233?nayan enersati was\u233?rmboghkaf njamke, f\u233?m norayati f\u233?yotaro y\u233?m m\u233?inyotio m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i yas\u233?mbotam Yurane gh\u233?ng\u233?n kitar\u233?. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
F\u233?m norayati, "Taik\u233?r y\u233?m s\u225?i yausafotam Yurai, " a f\u233?mofem mine efurnati y\u225?ne wafar\u233?gh si, noraye njafar fiyarafene Yur\u233?. "Nemnati y\u233?n\u233?mam\u233?n! Orom\u233?n w\u233?r\u225?r a akny\u233?ghkaf a enjnef\u233? t\u233? erametati m\u233?n\u225?t gh\u233?ng\u233?not! So y\u233?ndon taumyon f\u233?feta nden\u233? s\u225?fot gh\u233?ng\u233?n ram\u233?gh?" Yuram emote.
