F\u233?yo soram\u233? t\u225?f f\u233?m so mat kamndangi y\u233?nd y\u233?n\u233? kw\u233?n emo t\u233?ngwafarete y\u233?n\u233? matot m\u233?n\u225?t tane arn\u233?gh Lefi \u225?rf\u233? so m\u233? y\u233?ng\u233?m, " noraye njafar fiyarafene Yur\u233?.
