"Y\u233?nd w\u233?m Yur\u233?, a y\u233?nd yau f\u233?nataye k\u225?y\u225?ton. Y\u233?n\u233? t\u233?fnan f\u233?m Jeikofene \u225?kiambum yau m\u233? ewalinday\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 7\~}
K\u233?tamayo f\u233?fene \u225?kifene efogh k\u233?s tanmorw\u233?n, f\u233?mofem t\u233? takenaw\u233?t tane n\u225?k a t\u225?ik\u233?rofnar tamorw\u233?n waitogh\u233?t. S\u233?nonjo k\u233?nangongi tafaf, a y\u233?nd w\u233?i so k\u233?nangon f\u233?fefaf, " njafar fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 W\u233?nde f\u233?m namotati, 'Y\u233?nd n\u233?mam\u233?n so nangotam t\u225?f y\u233?nd yau \u225?ndan y\u233?nyotam nayu?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 8\~}
"Sp \u225?r\u233?m kembneye yambnat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n? M\u233? f\u233?mofem t\u233? kembneye kwambnati!
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "W\u233?nde f\u233?m namotati, 'F\u233?mon n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?s\u233?rmbne?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "F\u233?mofem t\u233? kembneye kwambnati \u225?mbiro 10m\u233?n k\u233?m\u233?ghan a ram\u233?gh \u225?mb y\u225?yot. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 9\~}
F\u233?m m\u233?inyotio em mbawaran, f\u233?fene Yuram t\u233? kembne kwambne y\u233?nd. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 10\~}
En\u233?rsati m\u233?inyotio \u225?mbiro 10m\u233?n y\u233?nan wam\u225?ng\u233?gh m\u233?ngot m\u233?n\u225?t k\u233?t\u233? so y\u233?m njamke f\u233?yotaro tane w\u225?wefnogh m\u233?ngon. Njam f\u233?mofem yafrotati, " njafar fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye, "Y\u233?ndon so efenan njafaran s\u233?safne f\u233?feyot. Y\u233?ndon so y\u233?nmasunan freng\u233?gh ndimbale f\u233?fene m\u233?ngo sat\u233? so em afoghare sifayafnar! Tufotangi! Kw\u233?kmangi ufoghan! {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 11\~}
"F\u233?fene njamke t\u233?f\u233?n so y\u233?m t\u225?rf\u225?r, y\u233?ndon so ewambetan k\u233?tam\u233? gh\u233?njta a gh\u233?njneta, f\u233?fene mbwe yau so m\u233? naf\u233?rnat tikfan, " njafar fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 12\~}
"F\u233?yo m\u233?inyotio mband maratam so n\u233?mndetat freng\u233?gh, f\u233?fene mband so y\u233?m m\u233?ndef\u233?, " njafar fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 13\~}
"F\u233?m t\u233? korayati m\u225?m\u225?fi si tanem\u233?n, " Yur\u233? noraye.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 "W\u233?nde f\u233?m norayati, 'F\u233?mo n\u233?m\u233? y\u233?s\u233?rmbne? N\u233?m\u233? si y\u233?nd korayam fefaf?'
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 14\~}
"F\u233?m t\u233? korayati n\u233?m\u233? mer y\u233?m s\u225?i n\u233?usenam Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne? N\u233?m\u233? \u225?mb y\u233?ndfem yanang\u233?m m\u233?n\u225?yan tanwaitotam y\u225?ne wafar\u233?gh si o m\u233?n\u225?t y\u233?ta s\u225?i tauyafong\u233?m njafar fiyafene Yurai nden\u233? y\u233?nd gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsis\u233? y\u233?n\u233?m t\u233?fene yuafiyamm\u233?n? {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 15\~}
Y\u233?nam\u233? s\u233?nonjo y\u233?ndfem so emndetam awarmbogh t\u233?fn\u225?r freng\u233?gh, f\u225? emofem ewafrotat yaufi n\u233?n\u225?y\u225?totat wem\u225?r, a f\u225? emofem yufotat Ng\u225?nj\u225?n m\u233?n\u225?t s\u225?i ekmeta f\u225? k\u233?rtayan w\u233?nde yau em t\u233?kratan."'
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Yurane efalo y\u225?togh si gh\u233?rgh\u233?rsisam\u233?n
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 16\~}
F\u233?yo y\u233?n\u233? \u225?r emofem f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? t\u233?fandaw\u233?t Yur\u233? korayaw\u233?t f\u225?rof\u225?ro, a Yur\u233? n\u225?y\u225?rai n\u233?m\u233? f\u225? korayaw\u233?t. Y\u225?ne saf\u233?n, a awafarogh\u233?t bukan t\u233? efarotam\u233?nd m\u233?n\u225?t ersam\u233?nd y\u233?tkw\u233?n emofem f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? t\u233?fandaw\u233?t a t\u250?m\u233?n mwigh\u233? tamorw\u233?n m\u233?n\u225?t y\u225?ne y\u233?tkw\u233?nan eus\u233?nan\u233?gh.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 17\~}
"F\u225? so em tane \u225?r, "njafar fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye. "Y\u233?n\u233? efghon njam y\u233?ndo siya yafrotan mogh, f\u225? so em tane f\u233?nataye ngonj\u233?lot. Y\u233?ndon so ewarawenan f\u225? nden\u233? f\u233?t\u233? y\u233?ferafafem y\u233?nau ewarawenat \u225?y\u225?rgh\u233?tk\u233?r ro ambum. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 18\~}
F\u233?yo f\u233?mofem w\u233?ikor so tawinjongi f\u233?natayero mbark\u225?nd \u225?r a yaufi \u225?r, y\u233?n\u233? n\u233?ndk\u233?fan emofem yausafotat Ng\u225?nj\u225?ne a emofem yau.
\par\pard\plain \s52\ql\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs33 4
\par\pard\plain \s105\qc\fi0\lin0\rin0\sb160\sa80\b\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 Mogh efogh y\u233?n\u233?m
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 1\~}
Njafar Fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye, "Mogh efogh y\u233?n\u233?m, nakerne ndenanit f\u233?s areng. Y\u233?n\u233? efghon awarmbogh \u225?r a yaufiyam \u225?r so nak\u233?rnat ndenanit mbangmbang. F\u225? so tawifong\u233?- s\u233?r\u233?mb, kafekafe, a m\u233?inyotio.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 2\~}
W\u233?nde f\u233?feyot emofem f\u233?rf\u233?raf\u233? y\u233?fandati tane y\u233?tkw\u233?n, mbark\u225?nd yamm\u233?n efogh so kanong\u233? freng\u233?ghaf\u233? y\u225?ne njamban. A f\u233?m so kuwanongi yuweke natnati \u225?uw\u233?ghaf\u233? ndenanit tos\u233? kau y\u233?nau taitorngi yus n\u233?ne sifayafaf. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 3\~}
Y\u233?n\u233? efghon y\u233?ndo \u225?nde so yam ewafrotan, f\u233?mofem so esenati yaufiyamaf\u233? \u225?r faknit f\u233?fene kafkaf mbanmbanan, " njafar fiyarafene Yur\u233? noraye.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 4\~}
Nawafarotati m\u233?n\u225?t siya ewaitotati Mosesene n\u225?k, tane \u225?s\u225?fogh t\u233?fn\u225?roene m\u233?inyotio wafar\u233?gh\u233?t a n\u225?kn\u225?k y\u233?n\u233? y\u233?ndon \u225?rk\u233? yaramay\u233?n k\u233?t\u233? mband tunakfan Sainai m\u233?inyotio Israil \u225?r\u233?t.
\par\pard\plain \s60\ql\fi180\lin0\rin0\sb0\sa0\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\nosupersub\cf2\fs22 {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 5\~}
N\u233?retati, y\u233?ndon yengwafaretan Ng\u225?nj\u225?nene mat y\u225?togh Elaija soram\u233? ndimbal wasneng\u233?gh efogh kufarng\u233? Yurane. {\cs57\b0\i0\ul0\scaps0\super\cf2\fs22 6\~}
Y\u225?ne watamegham so ewawenangote y\u233?ferafafene tik\u233?f y\u233?fene ambumafefaf, a ambumafene tik\u233?f k\u233?t\u225?n y\u233?ferafafefaf m\u233?nam\u233?n y\u233?nd m\u233?t\u233? w\u233?n\u233?m a mbaware t\u233?sman yu."}
